The crypto market is still young and growing. Anything can happen at any moment. On the one hand, this makes the market quite unpredictable. But on the other hand, this makes it a field of financial opportunities. 2022 may be the best time to start investing in cryptos. The perspectives are inspiring, so with a proper strategy and a bit of luck, a trader may have a profitable trading year. 